title: Trap Games and Notable Matchups in Week 3
description:
Wendi Nix, Sam Acho, and 'Stanford' Steve Coughlin discuss some of Week three's notable matchups, including some potential trap games for Top 25 teams. Plus, Jay Walker and Tiffany Greene join the show to talk about an HBCU 'Clash of the Titans' between Grambling at Jackson State. Also, Doug Kezirian talks with Stanford Steve about some of the most intriguing betting lines in Week 3.
